TO RUN APP

For Server
    cd mern-exercise-tracker
    cd backend
    nodemon server

For App
    cd mern-exercise-tracker
    npm start



create react app without installing it
    npx create-react-app mern-exercise-tracker

Then go to -> cd mern-exercise-tracker

create new folder backend

terminal -> cd backend

Then create package.json by typing "npm init -y" for all yesin terminal

terminal -> npm install express cors mongoose dotenv
cors - cross origin resource sharing
dotenv - loads env vairable from .env file to process.env

installing globally -> npm install -g nodemon
it automatically restart node app when file changes in directory are detected

